PrecisAppointment of HUGH MORRIS, of Delta, British Columbia; LISA JEFFREY, of Montreal, Quebec; GEORGIA PE-PIPER, of Halifax, Nova Scoita; and PETER LOEWEN, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as members of the Natural Sciences and Engineering Research Council to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
